{"tid":1381974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1小時募集逾千頂頭盔高雄港生：部份係全新全罩式防護力強","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffabdb3aaaa708673d1e1c20799a28841ea8b3d","tid":1381974,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"在台灣高雄的香港女學生林沛晞，日前邀請了5、6名港生在高雄捷運站外募集500頂頭盔，才1個小時就收集逾千頂，還有10多萬元新台幣（下同，逾2.5萬港元）現金。她今天偕同1名男同學現身台灣基進高雄黨部，對高雄人的熱情和捐助表示感謝，並盼更多台灣人關心香港反送中運動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190729/59875420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59875420&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=0170bf97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59875420&h=deebaa5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190729/59875420</a>"},{"pid":"c39da6f3ba3bb9ee31de823bc8c85348dbd2d6f7","tid":1381974,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}